Subject: [87/99] vmscan: limit VM_EXEC protection to file pages
References: <20091106221358.309857998@mini.kroah.org>
Content-Disposition: inline; filename=vmscan-limit-vm_exec-protection-to-file-pages.patch
Content-Length: 1202
