Subject: [89/99] x86: mce: Fix thermal throttling message storm
References: <20091106221358.309857998@mini.kroah.org>
Content-Disposition: inline; filename=x86-mce-fix-thermal-throttling-message-storm.patch
Content-Length: 2091
